{"tid":898964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旅遊界議員倡遊客分流至屯門黃金海岸","createTime":"2018-11-12T05:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T15:59:44.000Z","uid":48973,"like":5,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"e4c01c96188ed1235ad551f8658078f67e6a4627","tid":898964,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181112/58902898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181112%2F58902898&d=Jjls0yldg%2BbC47GMtSCu9zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1839fdb6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181112%2F58902898&h=262d7bbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181112/58902898</a><br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋通車後大批內地團湧港逼爆東涌，當中內地團疑似由無牌導遊非法帶團，令東涌遊客人數劇增，立法會旅遊界議員姚思榮今早於電台節目表示，政府針對東涌遊客增加的措施已見成效，並建議政府向內地反映無牌導遊等問題，同時本地旅遊業界亦應研究疏導安排，如分流至屯門黃金海岸和新田購物城。<br />\n姚思榮認為，東涌遊客多並非新鮮事：「好多遊客去機場之前一個短暫停留點」，但認為超過臨界點令居民承受不到，建議業界「做多啲產品」，如「（屯門）黃金海岸或落馬洲新田（購物城）同佢哋傾一傾，反正（遊客）都係嚟買嘢。」<br />\n至於內地領隊違規帶團的問題，姚思榮認為，政府應向內地當局反映，加強懲處屢勸不改的旅行社及領隊，高調進行拘捕及檢控行動，以起阻嚇作用。"},{"pid":"d960208c115df3e3618924bb8369bee2549bbbdf","tid":898964,"uid":52006,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:18:48.000Z","msg":"到時就真係變黃金海岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05b05d788c580a415ac80b530c9c975a0dde9f5","tid":898964,"uid":8392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:19:28.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母呀"},{"pid":"a41bd54d2a120c794a7f1ae0197e36c5c0efdc0c","tid":898964,"uid":24050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d960208c115df3e3618924bb8369bee2549bbbdf","tid":898964,"uid":52006,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T05:18:48.000Z","msg":"到時就真係變黃金海岸<img